        <mxCell id="note" value="DATA FLOW NOTES:&#xa;• No VPC required (all API calls over public HTTPS endpoints)&#xa;• No data stored persistently (audit logs to stdout only)&#xa;• Credentials: AWS CLI profile / SSO / IAM Role&#xa;• All API calls use TLS 1.2+ encryption in transit&#xa;• No customer data leaves the account (runs locally)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#F2F3F4;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontColor=#232F3E;rounded=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="520" width="400" height="100" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
